<p begin="00:02:58.312" end="00:03:02.149" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WITH JUSTICE SCALIA WRITING A </span><span style="block">BLISTERING DEFENSE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:03:02.149" end="00:03:02.616" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; YES.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:02.616" end="00:03:03.617" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BIG SURPRISE.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:03.617" end="00:03:04.952" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">SCALIA WASN'T HAPPY.</span></p>
<p begin="00:03:04.952" end="00:03:11.158" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">HE FIRMLY BELIEVES THAT IT IS </span><span style="block">INAPPROPRIATE AND ARROGANT FOR </span><span style="block">THE COURT TO STRIKE DOWN A</span></p>


